  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_recap_body",
    "type": "recap",
    "speaker": "talkover",
    "content": "威尔再次来访，两人达成和解。他尊重她的选择。她决定回归家庭。爱能包容。握手言和。难道爱能包容所有的差异……",
    "pause_ms": 1500
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00002",
    "type": "dialogue",
    "speaker": "维达",
    "gender": "female",
    "content": "还多得很呢。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00003",
    "type": "dialogue",
    "speaker": "维达",
    "gender": "female",
    "content": "也许有一天我们在这里会看到像你刚才所说的那种脑满肠肥而又愤世嫉俗的法国人（多么可怕，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00004",
    "type": "dialogue",
    "speaker": "维达",
    "gender": "female",
    "content": "净是喜欢冷嘲热讽，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00005",
    "type": "dialogue",
    "speaker": "维达",
    "gender": "female",
    "content": "满身散发出烟草味，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00006",
    "type": "dialogue",
    "speaker": "维达",
    "gender": "female",
    "content": "拼命喝烈酒，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00007",
    "type": "dialogue",
    "speaker": "维达",
    "gender": "female",
    "content": "把脑子和消化器官都给毁掉了！",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00008",
    "type": "dialogue",
    "speaker": "维达",
    "gender": "female",
    "content": "），",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00009",
    "type": "dialogue",
    "speaker": "维达",
    "gender": "female",
    "content": "不过，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00010",
    "type": "dialogue",
    "speaker": "维达",
    "gender": "female",
    "content": "谢谢老天爷，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00011",
    "type": "dialogue",
    "speaker": "维达",
    "gender": "female",
    "content": "我们暂时还得忙着修草坪和铺路面！",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00012",
    "type": "dialogue",
    "speaker": "维达",
    "gender": "female",
    "content": "你知道，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00013",
    "type": "dialogue",
    "speaker": "维达",
    "gender": "female",
    "content": "这些事情真的一转眼就会来了。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00014",
    "type": "dialogue",
    "speaker": "维达",
    "gender": "female",
    "content": "妇女读书会好歹已是初见成效。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00015",
    "type": "dialogue",
    "speaker": "维达",
    "gender": "female",
    "content": "而你呢？",
    "pause_ms": 1000
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00016",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "卡萝尔到处听人说，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00017",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "这场战争将在人们心理上引起一种根本性的变化；",
    "pause_ms": 400
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00018",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "所有一切事物，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00019",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "从婚姻关系一直到国家政体，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00020",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "都会在道德上得到净化和提高。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00021",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "对于这种变化，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00022",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "她觉得非常高兴，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00023",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "不过她始终没有发现它罢了。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00024",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "她看到镇上妇女们已把桥牌扔掉，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00025",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "正在给红十字会做纱布绷带，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00026",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "同时还笑着说，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00027",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "没有白糖叫她们怎么过日子呢。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00028",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "不过，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00029",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "她们在做这些外科包扎用的敷料时，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00030",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "并没有谈到什么上帝和凡夫俗子的灵魂，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00031",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "她们只不过唠唠叨叨地谈到迈尔斯·伯恩斯塔姆的粗鲁无礼，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00032",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "特里·古尔德四年以前跟一个庄稼人的女儿之间有过私情，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00033",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "以及怎么烧卷心菜，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00034",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "怎样修改短褂子等。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00035",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "她们一提到战争，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00036",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "只是一个劲儿谈它残暴恐怖。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00037",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "卡萝尔去做纱布绷带，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00038",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "不但很守时刻，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00039",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "而且效率还很高，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00040",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "但她怎么也没法像莱曼·卡斯太太和博加特太太那样，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00041",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "给那些绷带、",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00042",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "敷料灌满了同仇敌忾的情绪。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00043",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "她对维达愤愤不平地说：",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00044",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "“年轻人都在努力工作，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00045",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "而这些老奶奶却坐在一边，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00046",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "净跟我们打岔，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00047",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "一开口话里就充满了憎恨，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00048",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "毕竟是她们身体太虚弱，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00049",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "什么事儿都不干了，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00050",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "只会憎恨别人吧。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00051",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "”\n但维达马上转过身来对她说：",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00052",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "“你即使不向她们表示一点儿敬意，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00053",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "至少也不应该如此冒失无礼，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00054",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "一味固执己见；",
    "pause_ms": 400
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00055",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "要知道现下这个时刻，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00056",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "有许许多多的男女正在面临着死亡。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00057",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "我们当中有些人——我们已经作出了这么多的贡献，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00058",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "而且又都是乐于这么做的。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00059",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "最低要求我们希望——你们这些人可不要自作聪明，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00060",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "净是损人呀。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00061",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "”\n接下来是卡萝尔的哭泣声。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00062",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "卡萝尔从心里确实希望看到普鲁士独裁政府的垮台；",
    "pause_ms": 400
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00063",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "她自己深信，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00064",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "除了普鲁士以外，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00065",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "世界上哪儿都没有独裁政府了；",
    "pause_ms": 400
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00066",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "她从电影上一看到部队从纽约出发的情景，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00067",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "心情就感到非常亢奋；",
    "pause_ms": 400
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00068",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "可是叫她深感不安的，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00069",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "却是她在街上遇着迈尔斯·伯恩斯塔姆，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00070",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "听到他说了下面这些话：",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00071",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "“你的那些事儿怎么样？",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00072",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "我呢，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00073",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "混得还不错，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00074",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "新近又买了两头大母牛。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00075",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "怎么啦，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00076",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "这会儿你变成了一个爱国者？",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00077",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "啊？",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00078",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "准定是他们带来的民主——死亡的民主。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00079",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "是的，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00080",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "打从伊甸园那个时候开始，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00081",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "只要一打仗，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00082",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "工人们总是根据大老板说给他们听的冠冕堂皇的理由，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00083",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "奔赴战场，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00084",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "互相残杀。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00085",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "可现在我比从前聪明了，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00086",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "我已经学乖了，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00087",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "什么战争不战争，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00088",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "我压根儿不乐意听呢。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00089",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "”\n卡萝尔一听到迈尔斯这些话以后，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_038_00090",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "心里考虑的已不再是这场战争的问题，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
